    <div class="about">
        <div class="HEAD">ABOUT US</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Established in the year 2021, All India Sports Training Academy is one of Jabalpur's leading sports club with
            provision for a variety of outdoor sports facilities namely: archery, athletics, cricket, weightlifting,
            wrestling, football and swimming. Situated at IIIT JABALPUR, Jabalpur, the academy has been built on a 250
            acre area and has all the latest state of the art sporting equipment's. With excellent amenities and other
            facilities in place, we are proud to say that All India Sports Training Academy is the finest sports
            training centre in the entire Jabalpur area. The academy believes in providing quality training at
            affordable costs. Having said this, the academy focuses on constant up gradation and enhancement of
            infrastructure on a regular basis without making the services exorbitant. The renowned coach's and trainers
            on the academy's panel make the academy a trusted name amongst athletes and budding sportsmen Founded by Mr.
            Sanjeev Jain, All India Sports Training Academy has been actively training and grooming aspiring sportsmen
            to achieve a higher level of excellence.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="visionmissionhead">Vision & Mission</div>
    <img src="images\vision.png" style="position:absolute;margin-left:50px;margin-top:40px;height:100px;width:150px;">
    <div class="vision">To identify, nurture and sharpen inside an individual for sports while moulding the performance
        for a winning streak and make winning a habit.</div>

    <img src="images\mission.png" style="position:absolute;margin-left:50px;margin-top:250px;height:100px;width:150px;">

    <div class="mission">To be the first choice of budding sportsmen and ensure a growing presence through setting
        leadership standards, performance and customer satisfaction in the field of sports.</div>

